 Don't you know what eight years mean? 

75
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:06,120
 It's the time it takes for a child to be born and go to elementary school. 

76
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:09,640
 We're breaking up like this after all that time? In one breath? 

77
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:12,920
 It's not like we were just messing around! 

78
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:19,950
 Whether we were together eight years or eight weeks, 

79
00:07:20,860 --> 00:07:23,730
 breakups are the same. 

80
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:28,410
 Goodbye. So long. 

81
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:31,680
 That's the end of it, Eun Ho. 

82
