I have already met and spoken with Press Director Soh.

111
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:52,210
 Hello. 

112
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:54,600
 You don't have an appointment today. 

113
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:58,990
