00:23:36,700 --> 00:23:40,730
 Working here is not possible. 

262
00:23:40,730 --> 00:23:43,480
 We don't need more workers. 

263
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,900
 One person is enough. 

264
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:49,540
 I'm also not allowed to get paid elsewhere. 

265
00:23:49,540 --> 00:23:51,410
 I already belong to a company. 

266
00:23:51,410 --> 00:23:55,030
 Then why do you want to do this? 

267
